    "description": "Evergreen India Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Supply Chain Manager for our Delhi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Evergreen India Ventures Solutions:\nEvergreen India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Evergreen India Ventures Solutions!",
